niceName: Fourth of July Marching Drum (Sound Pack)
niceDesc: Celebrate the Declaration of Independence on July 4th 1776 by marching on the spot in time to the beat of your massive magical invisible star spangled drum.
Author: munki

niceName: Fourth of July Marching Whistle (Sound Pack)
niceDesc: Celebrate the Declaration of Independence on July 4th 1776 by marching on the spot with a war wounded limp and a soulful tune - like t was 1776.
Author: munki

niceDesc: A collection of 3 air-mic animations, with voice samples which can be heard by other avatars near you. Your avatar can sing lyrically, rock and chant Yeah yeah , or croon Oooh yeah. . Press square for the contextual menu, to choose the sound sample and its associated animation.
Author: Tanguy
